// OOPs = Object Oriented Programming system 
// It is a way of writing code where we 
// --> group data(property)
// --> and functions(method)
// inside the object 
// Javascript is Prototype based language ,but it suppoerts oops using class contructor function and prototypes 
// why OOPs in javascript 
// --> Code becomes clean and structured 
// --> Easy to reuse  
// --> Easy to maintain 
// --> Easy to scale  large application 

// Object --> collection of property and member is called the object 

